The paper deals with evaluating navigation agents that interpret natural language instructions and navigate through an environment, which falls under the domain of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) and Reinforcement Learning (cs.LG) for navigation. Additionally, the paper involves computer vision techniques for interpreting the environment (cs.CV) and robotics for physical navigation (cs.RO).
